  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nI don't know, but it's a huge different between `setState` and `useState`\r\n\r\n**What is the current behavior?**\r\n\r\nWe know, React doesn't batch update in asynchronous functions. But I find that in hooks, the `useState` will batch update in async functions.\r\n\r\nI just want to know, is it a change not mentioned in the documentation?\r\n\r\nYou can see the different in the [this](https://codesandbox.io/s/43n9kk4597)",
